The Simple Roleplay Hub.description:
Tired of complicated RP hubs?
Do you want to find new and great RP servers?
Are you a server owner and you just want a simple everyone ping to advertise your server?
Look no further than the **Simple Roleplay Hub!** 
This ad like the server will be kept simple. 
We will ping everyone regardless of size and we have 6 different tiers depending on the size of your server. 

What are you waiting for? Join today!
